window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Everything is finally coming together in Sam Archer’s life, and yet simultaneously, the delicate balance is becoming strained. He is well aware that his relationships are heading toward a breaking point if something doesn’t give - and soon.</p> <p>However, when new threats appear, everyone finally realizes that a decision must be made. One that will change his life forever.<br> The balancing act cannot go on.</p> <p>Will Sam’s family be able to endure the drastic changes coming to their lives? And when help comes from an unexpected source, will they be able to band together to conquer their enemies?</p> <p>Warning: This book contains adult content that may not be suitable for all audiences, including adult scenes and harem elements.</p>"; 
